{"tid":1884983,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次同老婆整Ebook, 睇下大家有無咩好意見?","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T10:15:04.000Z","uid":235547,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"434760cde9a8b1ba43c146f97a0c8e531db9833e","tid":1884983,"uid":235547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:24:31.000Z","msg":"我老婆寫左一系列既兒童書Ebook, 對象係幼兒至六歲小朋友。教小朋友執拾, 日常生活既嘢<br />\n, 順便學埋英文。<br />\n<br />\n我地寫左個網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://itutors.wixsite.com/itotsbooks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitutors.wixsite.com%2Fitotsbooks&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=4288a8ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itutors.wixsite.com/itotsbooks</a><br />\n<br />\n而每本書都有相應工作紙比小朋友做, Subscribe個Mailing list就會有。Youtube Channel, Facebook 都寫埋。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/itotsbooks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fitotsbooks%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=2432bd2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/itotsbooks/</a><br />\n<br />\n宜家第一集暫時放左喺Amazon 賣緊, 但呢度應該有師兄可能做呢行或者有經驗, 所以都想睇下有無咩意見可以比到我地。<br />\n<br />\n感激萬分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb52acd3649f59e79b5f6d842854ecc1f170adca","tid":1884983,"uid":244876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"以前學過少少Ebook<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得如果想家長買<br />\n最少都可以整本demo 比人download  話可能比頭兩三頁d家長用下<br />\n同埋想問係咪pdf format定ebook格式(即係可能用Indesign之類整)?<br />\n<br />\n咁問係因為家長應該會用Tablet 電話等去比小朋友睇<br />\n睇條片睇唔出有冇咩互動功能(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我skip來睇)<br />\n如果有互動功能最好比到家長睇下<br />\n細路會終意有d野玩下學下會開心d<br />\n<br />\n同埋呢個網站下面d人既評語個排版<br />\n置中好似睇得唔係咁舒服?(個人意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"9d1fbe03b24f5683af11d530cb922556aa379d7a","tid":1884983,"uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"